
wiki:nevada Reno is the thirdlargest city in Nevada (Behind Las Vegas and Henderson), and a popular destination for Northern California gambling gamblers.  Reno is about adventures outside of Davis 2 hours driving distance from Davis (approximately 144 miles).

The Reno region is one of the closest prostitution venues for Davis and Sacramento residents, but prostitution in http://www.cityofreno.com/ Reno itself (as with all the larger counties in Nevada) is illegal.  Still, visiting Reno can be an educational experience for any Davis native, with its tall illuminated buildings that waste ridiculous amounts of electricity and mediocre public transportation.

Also home to the wiki:WikiPedia:University_of_Nevada,_Reno University of Nevada Reno, the first of Nevadas two universities.
